com.Netzwerk.de

Class ServerThread

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.Netzwerk.de.ServerThread
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class ServerThread
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable
    This class describe how the client would be handle and which commands can use the client.
    This commands can the client use

    -getip by name type
    -getip by name
    -getip save type
    -getip balance type
    -gettyp all
    -gettyp type
    -help
    -exit (to close the connection)
    Version:
    0.0.1
    Author:
    Pascal Sch√§fer
